3.00	Civilization_and_its_Discontents	Civilization and Its Discontents	Civilization and Its Discontents is a book by Sigmund Freud. Written in 1929, and first published in German in 1930 as Das Unbehagen in der Kultur ("The Uneasiness in Culture"), it is considered one of Freud's most important and widely read works.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a3/Freud_Unbehagen_Kultur_1930.jpg/220px-Freud_Unbehagen_Kultur_1930.jpg
